    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> July 1, 2026</p>

    <p>Thank you for using <strong>Bullion Premium</strong> ("the App").</p>

    <p>This Privacy Policy explains what information is collected when you use the App and how that information is handled.</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>

    <p>Bullion Premium does not require user registration and does not intentionally collect, store, or transmit personally identifiable information such as your name, email address, phone number, or location.</p>

    <p>The App does not create user profiles or maintain user accounts.</p>

    <h2>Market Data</h2>

    <p>To provide precious metal pricing and related market information, the App communicates with third-party data providers through secure internet connections.</p>

    <p>When your device requests market data, the service provider may automatically receive technical information required for normal internet communication, such as your IP address, request timestamps, and other standard network metadata. This information is handled by the respective service provider according to its own privacy practices.</p>

    <p>Bullion Premium does not use this information to identify individual users.</p>

    <h2>In-App Purchases</h2>

    <p>If you choose to purchase premium features, payments are processed exclusively by Apple through the App Store.</p>

    <p>Bullion Premium does not receive or store your payment card information or other payment credentials.</p>

    <h2>Analytics</h2>

    <p>At this time, Bullion Premium does not use third-party analytics services to track user behavior within the App.</p>

    <h2>Data Storage</h2>

    <p>The App may store settings and preferences locally on your device to improve your experience. This information remains on your device and is not transmitted to our servers.</p>

    <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>

    <p>Bullion Premium is not specifically directed toward children under the age of 13. The App does not knowingly collect personal information from children.</p>

    <h2>Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>

    <p>This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time. Any changes will be reflected by updating the "Last updated" date at the top of this page.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>

    <p>If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy, you may contact the developer at:</p>

